================================
 Chromium OS build environments
================================

These are a collection of environments used to successfully build Chromium OS

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
  host.sh
    Host machine build environment.

  chroot.sh
    Chroot environment.

  crypt.sh
    This environment is for the cryptmount script.
    For more information about cryptmount, see cryptmount --help.
    (This is probably not needed)

  server.sh
    This is used by the dev_server command for ota updates, etc.
    For more information about devserver, see dev_server --help.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To automatically source environments:

 On the host machine:
   Copy: host.profile to ~/.profile

 Inside the chroot:
   Copy chroot.bashrc to ~/.bashrc

